                         Comments? We welcome them!

   This server and data are not considered "operational". We do not
   guarantee availability or timely delivery of data and the server should
   not be used to support operational observation, forecasting, emergency,
   or disaster mitigation operations, either public or private. We also do
   not provide weather forecasts at this site, that is the mission of the
   National Weather Service, please contact them for forecast information.
       _______________________________________________________________

                   Information and how to use this server
       _______________________________________________________________

   The options on the left will take you to a specific set of sectors.
   Each browsable image from this web site is a 'clickable' link to the
   full 640x480 image.

   You can view retrospective imagery, for the past 21 days, by selecting
   the 'GOES 8 Archive' or the 'GOES 10 Archve' choice on the left side of
   the screen. Use your back button on your browser to come back to this
   page to look at other images or links.
   We have installed text descriptions for most of our links that will pop
   up over the icon as you move across a selectable area.
